<div class=\"space-y-2\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-3 py-1 text-[0.72rem] font-medium tracking-[0.13em] uppercase transition-colors border-border/70 bg-background/52 text-foreground/62 backdrop-blur-sm backdrop-saturate-[1.3]\">Release feed</div><p class=\"max-w-2xl text-sm leading-7 text-foreground/62\">Newest first. Clear versioning. Enough context to explain what changed and why.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-6\"></div></div></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"relative overflow-hidden border-t border-border/60 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,var(--surface-1),var(--surface-2))] py-14 backdrop-blur-xl backdrop-saturate-[1.5]\"><div class=\"absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-primary/28 to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl px-5 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-10\"><div class=\"grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr_0.8fr]\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><img src=\"/icon-purple.svg\" class=\"h-8 w-auto text-primary/70\" alt=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" loading=\"eager\" decoding=\"async\"/><p class=\"font-heading text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-foreground/62\">Sonicverse</p></div><h2 class=\"max-w-md text-3xl leading-[1.08] font-medium tracking-[-0.03em] text-balance\">Modern software systems, digital products, and open-source technology.</h2><p class=\"max-w-xl text-sm leading-7 text-foreground/62\">Built with strong engineering taste, open collaboration, and a preference for systems that stay understandable as they grow.</p></div><div><p class=\"mb-4 text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.04em] text-foreground/76\">Navigation</p><div class=\"grid gap-2 text-sm text-foreground/62\"><a class=\"hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a><a class=\"hover:text-foreground\"